%% title: Safety incident || module: Safety || role: Field worker / WHS || status: DRAFT || view: module
flowchart TD
  start([Incident occurs on site]):::startEnd --> open[Field worker opens incident form on mobile]:::process
  open --> capture[/Capture details, photos, GPS/]:::io
  capture --> submit[Submit incident<br/>IS-INC auto-number]:::process
  submit --> notify[Notify Marco and safety admin]:::process
  notify --> sev{Severity extreme?}:::decision
  sev -- Yes --> stop[Stop work and immediate escalation]:::process
  sev -- No --> triage[Standard triage]:::process
  stop --> investigate[Investigate root cause]:::process
  triage --> investigate
  investigate --> actions[Assign corrective actions]:::process
  actions --> closed{Actions complete?}:::decision
  closed -- No --> actions
  closed -- Yes --> close[Close incident]:::doc
  close --> dash([Safety dashboard and report]):::output
